snippet.title: Alchemic Cutie PAX East 2020
snippet.description:
Alchemic Cutie is a relaxing adventure RPG set on colorful Wimba Island; while taming wild jellies you’ll meet villagers, enter jelly competitions and uncover the secrets of the island!

Check out our demo at the Indie Megabooth at PAX East 2020 on Sat 29th Feb & Sun 1st Mar.

Join the Cutie Club for more info @ https://alchemiccutie.com/

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/913720/Alchemic_Cutie/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/alchemiccutie
Facebook: http://facebook.com/alchemiccutie
